{"tid":1124584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"kai 同 krystal 的十年情 （多圖）","createTime":"2019-04-25T06:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T20:00:31.000Z","uid":222068,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ed9c99d1f0b8b4034b9c9e7650d9f33878397252","tid":1124584,"uid":222068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:21:52.000Z","msg":"樓主曾經是他們兩個的cp飯（現在不是） 在沒有公布戀愛前已經想他們在一起 <br />\nkai和krystal無論在外形、氣場、性格、品味都十分相似 而且都是94年生 是同齡親故。雖然公佈戀情13個月後就分手了  但應該是目前為止韓國idol界最為人津津樂道的一對情侶，所以樓主想整理以下他們相識到分手的經過。如果文筆不流暢、有錯別字請指正，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">部分cap圖會有蝗語，因為只找到大陸翻譯組翻譯。</span></span><br />\n<br />\nkrystal被SM娛樂星探發掘，2006年正式進入公司做練習生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fc6c0kh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFc6c0kh.jpg&h=d815fb9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKai在2007年通過SM娛樂青少年BEST選拔大會以舞蹈組第一名及人氣獎，進入SM娛樂做練習生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p896kkA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp896kkA.jpg&h=b9f29698&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次同框是12年3月w korea 雜誌拍攝，中間的是krystal，左邊藍色衣服的是kai，很可惜只有一張照片。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4hcfWX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4hcfWX.jpg&h=8064d512&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後是7月在LA的sm家族演唱會，這次有互動了，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">很多cp飯就是從這裡開始的</span></span></span>。<br />\n偷看<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wishnote.tw/500/2016/04/01/500_295715_1459507432.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wishnote.tw%2F500%2F2016%2F04%2F01%2F500_295715_1459507432.gif&h=ef5ec623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8AwgHF5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8AwgHF5.jpg&h=69df2d74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一起拖手鞠躬（krystal 主動）<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2016/04/01/5fcfb2d0c7e7d093bfdbe82e3eb991261459507216.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2016%2F04%2F01%2F5fcfb2d0c7e7d093bfdbe82e3eb991261459507216.gif&h=de33c4c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到了8月， S.M.ART EXHIBITION <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zDt3nHw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzDt3nHw.jpg&h=8ae7bcf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n還有sm家族演唱會 兩人之間沒有交流 那時候應該不是太熟<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgsrc.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=8552c705b4fd5266a72b3c1c9b199799/8c7bfbde9c82d158c826925f820a19d8bd3e422e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgsrc.baidu.com%2Fforum%2Fw%253D580%2Fsign%3D8552c705b4fd5266a72b3c1c9b199799%2F8c7bfbde9c82d158c826925f820a19d8bd3e422e.jpg&h=f00cfbf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n12年的糖就到這。<br />\n<br />\n之後到13年，應該每個exoL MeU都記得，當年很轟動的f(x)專輯Pink Tape內頁拍攝，SM竟然安排兩個大勢團體的人氣ACE一起拍情侶照。<br />\n主打曲<strong>初智齒</strong>（Rum Pum Pum Pum）：將真正的初戀比喻成排擠其他牙齒而長出的智齒 （智齒在韓國有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「愛牙」</span></strong>的意思，智齒一般是在談戀愛的年紀長出來的，並且長智齒的時候會疼，就<span style=\"color: red;\">像愛情的痛苦一樣</span>。）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8s3KRDf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8s3KRDf.jpg&h=74ca290d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8DZBHKV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8DZBHKV.jpg&h=aa8e27eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m7QtyRB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm7QtyRB.jpg&h=c0f695fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ObCDbDg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FObCDbDg.jpg&h=8112b843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NsoiV4X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNsoiV4X.jpg&h=e8e9d285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9wsLA4X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9wsLA4X.jpg&h=9c59b8ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如今在看，兩人的確很有初戀的感覺，還有krystal真的很配紅髮。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xhpx0wD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXhpx0wD.png&h=59ccb22f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後f(x)在電台宣傳時，被神童問到：為什麼會出現Kai呢？<br />\nkrystal回答：專輯本身是圍繞初戀來說的，他作為少女的初戀而出現的。<br />\n神童又問選擇Kai的理由是什麼呢？<br />\nkrystal回答：看起來挺合適的。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">期間一度非敬語叫了kai 的本名種仁，而不是藝名Kai，看來兩個人這時候已經挺熟路</span></span></span><br />\n神童再問：如果不是Kai的話，是別人的話，會選擇誰呢？除了Kai,我們公司的也好，其他公司的也好。好吧，不要我們公司的。<br />\n其他成員回答李勝基 宋鐘基 老師<br />\nkrystal回答：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我很滿足的。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">沒有說出其他男藝人的名字<br />\n</span> 甚至<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">pass掉神童提名的兩位男藝人</span>，李鍾碩、曾經的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">理想型孔侑</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uCUqqXs08MA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuCUqqXs08MA&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SSWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=4c7fdd67\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uCUqqXs08MA</a> 直接從31分開始看<br />\n<br />\n8月，Kai擔任人氣歌謠Mc，剛好碰上分f(x) 打歌。<br />\n這是彩排<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5cYu21m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5cYu21m.jpg&h=f9f78543&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nending encore <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">krystal主動揮手打招呼，注意表情</span></span> <br />\n<img src=\"http://imgsrc.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=5f566a0e74c6a7efb926a82ecdfbafe9/5e4913b5c9ea15ce8e942fd8b4003af33b87b258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgsrc.baidu.com%2Fforum%2Fw%253D580%2Fsign%3D5f566a0e74c6a7efb926a82ecdfbafe9%2F5e4913b5c9ea15ce8e942fd8b4003af33b87b258.jpg&h=ff410b5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://38.media.tumblr.com/15f7ffbb7f2e97803445f40229d56ab0/tumblr_mrcy98eXaK1qeukp1o3_250.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F38.media.tumblr.com%2F15f7ffbb7f2e97803445f40229d56ab0%2Ftumblr_mrcy98eXaK1qeukp1o3_250.gif&h=5a8c17d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">冰山公主？高冷？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f453175358cbc73dd696b331d5d2d34848880fa","tid":1124584,"uid":222068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:23:32.000Z","msg":"第一次開post 希望有人睇 唔好沉底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3129cabcdce5e3311b06cfff9834a0af7e6b87","tid":1124584,"uid":222068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:27:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75279471c9fc27e2d3a4e30340a5ba043720fa56","tid":1124584,"uid":222068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:28:16.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"aa4fb0100d435d2f1aca8da0f760f3ef3bd50e3f","tid":1124584,"uid":222068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:28:42.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"4f06e3b7b29d11461148b2f8ec80e34db863a3c9","tid":1124584,"uid":88168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69aef0da5b6258978b4394256db64395e37cb5a","tid":1124584,"uid":222068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:28:57.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"77ce73b592a50de2024c20ce67b7b2e